Hawan gaggawa na yawan kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Burtaniya tsakanin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Ƙididdigar yawan masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ya nuna irin wannan ci gaba a ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma a Burtaniya, wanda ya tabbatar da cewa, ko da yake a matakai daban-daban, cutar ta COVID-19 tana ci gaba cikin sauri a kowace ƙasa.
Bisa ga kwarewar Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da ma'aikatun kulawa mai tsanani suna bukatar su shirya don karuwar marasa lafiya da ke da cutar COVID-19 da ke bukatar kulawa, musamman kulawa mai tsanani.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an samu rahoton kamuwa da cutar huhu da ba a san dalilin ba a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cutar ta kasar Sin ta bayyana cewa kwayar cutar ta coronavirus ce wacce yanzu ake kira da SARS-CoV-2.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 an kira ta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
A yau, kusan kashi 80 cikin ɗari na waɗanda ke da COVID-19 suna da rashin lafiya, wato, kamuwa da numfashi tare da ko ba tare da ciwon huhu ba, kuma yawancin su suna warkewa.
A cikin kashi 14 cikin ɗari na cutar, COVID-19 na haifar da mummunar cuta da ke buƙatar asibiti, yayin da sauran kashi 6 cikin ɗari na cutar ke haifar da mummunar cuta da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Mutuwar marasa lafiya da ke asibiti saboda COVID-19 kusan kashi 4 ne.
A cikin wannan binciken, muna kimanta yadda cutar COVID-19 ta shafi ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU/EEA) da kuma Burtaniya (UK), kuma muna kwatanta shi da yadda cutar ta shafi lardin Hubei na ƙasar Sin.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a yanzu a ƙasashen EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya da na Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Al'ummar EU/EEA da Birtaniya sun kamu da cutar COVID-19
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya ci gaba da yaduwa, kuma halin da ake ciki na annobar COVID-19 a sauran ƙasashe na duniya yanzu haka yana bin wannan ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin fitowar 5 ga Maris na Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri da sauransu sun ba da rahoton farkon tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 a Turai bisa ga ma'anar cutar ta WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, an samu mutane uku na farko da aka tabbatar da cutar a Faransa a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020 a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano wasu mutane da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa 30 na EU/EEA da kuma a Burtaniya (UK) tare da, tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an samu mutum 39,768 da suka kamu da cutar da kuma mutum 1,727 da suka mutu, ciki har da mutane 17,750 da suka kamu da cutar da kuma mutane 1,441 da suka mutu a Italiya kadai.
Samun adadin da kuma yawan masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19
Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (CEPCM) tana sabunta adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda aka samo ne kawai daga tushen hukuma kamar ma'aikatar lafiya, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki na ƙasashe daban-daban da kuma WHO, a kowace rana da karfe 8:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan don kimanta yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya, da kuma kwatanta shi da kwarewar Italiya.
Don kimanta yaduwar masu cutar COVID-19, mun lissafa adadin adadin COVID-19 na kwanaki 14 a duniya, ta haka ne muka yi la'akari da yanayin COVID-19 a cikin kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya, daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma gwada adadin masu kamuwa da cutar da aka ruwaito a kowace ƙasa a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da karfe 8:00 na safe tare da bayanan Italiya na 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a ƙasashen EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya
Yanayin yawan mutane da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a kwanaki 14 a cikin EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya ya yi daidai da na lardin Hubei na kasar Sin (Hoto na 1).
A cikin EU/EEA da Birtaniya, adadin cutar COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a kusan 21 ga Fabrairu, sai ya ƙaru sosai a kusan 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (ƙarin bayanai).
Wannan canji ya kasance ne musamman saboda saurin karuwar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya sun nuna irin wannan karuwar yawan cutar COVID-19 (ƙarin bayanai).
Shafi na 2 ya nuna adadin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
An gano cewa a ranar 15 ga Maris, da karfe 8:00 na safe, wasu ƙasashe 15 na EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya sun riga sun ba da rahoton adadin adadin waɗanda suka kamu da cutar da ya yi daidai da na Italiya makonni 3 da suka gabata ko kuma ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin mutanen da aka ba da rahoton cutar COVID-19 na ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya.
Canjin yanayin cutar COVID-19 ya nuna cewa annobar tana ci gaba da irin wannan saurin a dukkan ƙasashe.
Kuma wannan duk da cewa ƙasashe suna cikin matakai daban-daban kuma akwai bambance-bambance a cikin martanin ma'aikatun kiwon lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa, da yiwuwar bambance-bambance a cikin ma'anar maganganun da kuma bambance-bambance a cikin ka'idojin zaɓar marasa lafiya da za a gwada don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da gwajin dawowa.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa na Italiya sun ce kusan kashi 10 cikin 100 na marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 na bukatar kulawa mai tsanani, kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ruwaito cewa asibitoci da sassan kulawa mai tsanani a yankunan sun riga sun kai iyakar ƙarfin su.
A halin yanzu ana samun bayanai kan shigar da mutane da cutar COVID-19 asibitoci da/ko sashen kula da masu ciwo mai tsanani a EU/EEA na kashi 6 cikin 100 da kuma kashi 1 cikin 100 na masu cutar (ba a gabatar da bayanai ba).
Duk da haka, akwai bukatar tattara bayanai a kai a kai domin a kara yawan bayanan da ake da su na sa ido a kan adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar da kuma mutuwar da suka faru.
Wani bincike da aka yi a shekara ta 201011 ya nuna cewa akwai babban bambanci a yawan gadaje da ake da su a cibiyoyin kulawa mai zurfi da na matsakaici a Turai, daga gadaje 29.2 a kowace mutum 100,000 a Jamus zuwa gadaje 4.2 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe suna da fiye ko ƙasa da albarkatu fiye da Italiya (12.5 gado a cikin kulawa mai zurfi da matsakaici a cikin mutane 100,000 a 2010).11
An samar da yanayin yin samfurin cikewar iyawar kulawa, tare da kimantawa ga kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya na yawan mutanen da ke shan magani da COVID-19 da ke da haɗarin sama da kashi 90 cikin 100 na wucewar iyawar gadajen kulawa mai tsanani a cikin sabuntawa ta shida na KARANTA KARANTA KARANTA KARANTA KARANTA COVID-19.
Tun da yake an tattara masu cutar a wasu yankuna na EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya, kuma asibitoci da kuma ma'aikatun kulawa mai tsanani suna kula da ƙididdigar al'ummar yankin, ya kamata a fi son a samar da bayanai kan masu cutar da kuma gadajen kulawa mai tsanani a matakin 2 na Ƙididdigar Ƙungiyoyin Ƙididdigar Ƙasa (NUTS 2).
Kwarewar Italiya da kuma ci gaban da ake samu a yanzu a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a cikin EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya.
Saboda haka, ƙasashe, asibitoci da ma'aikatun kulawa mai tsanani suna bukatar su shirya don yanayin watsa SARS-CoV-2 a cikin al'umma da kuma karuwar adadin marasa lafiya da ke da COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa, musamman kulawa mai tsanani, kamar yadda aka yi a yankunan da cutar ta shafa na Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin rahoton da CEPCM ta yi kwanan nan na gaggawa, gaggawa, da kuma cikakkiyar hanya na da muhimmanci wajen jinkirta yaduwar cutar SARS-COV-2, daga hanyar hanawa zuwa hanyar rage cutar, saboda karuwar yawan masu kamuwa da cutar da wuri-wuri ba zai ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci isasshen lokaci ba don fahimtar, yarda da kuma daidaita amsarsu, idan ba a aiwatar da wani abu ba a baya.
A cikin saurin tantance hadarin, an kuma lissafa matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a da za su iya rage tasirin annobar.
Akwai ɗan gajeren lokaci da kowace ƙasa za ta iya ƙara ƙoƙarin sarrafa cutar don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin lamba a kan ayyukan kiwon lafiya.
Idan ba haka ba, tsarin kiwon lafiya na sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA na iya fuskantar ƙaruwar marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wadda cutar coronavirus 2 mai saurin numfashi (SARS) (SARS-CoV-2) ta haifar, ta yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane sama da 3,000 da kuma kamuwa da mutane sama da 80,000 a China da sauran wurare a duniya, ta haifar da bala'in jin kai.
Kamar SARS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da dubban masu cutar SARS a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya yaduwa ta hanyar barewa kuma yana haifar da irin wannan alamun ta hanyar irin wannan tsarin.
