Rarraba ƙwayoyin cuta na ƙananan hanyoyin numfashi ne kawai aka yi a cikin marasa lafiya da suke da matsalar rashin garkuwar jiki.
An fara samun cutar SARS a ƙarshen shekara ta 2002 a lardin Guangdong na ƙasar Sin.
Ba tare da ƙididdigar masu watsawa ba, an kimanta cewa kowane mutum zai iya haifar da ƙananan mutane biyu tare da lokacin rufi tsakanin kwanaki 4 zuwa 7, tare da ƙaruwar ƙwayar cutar a ranar 10 na cutar.
Marasa lafiya da ke dauke da cutar SARS-CoV suna fara samun ciwon zuciya, ciwon kai, zazzabi, rashin jin daɗi da kuma jin kuncin jiki, sannan kuma suna samun rashin nutsuwa, tari da kuma wahalar numfashi a matsayin alamun bayyanar cututtuka.
