Cutar cutar ta numfashi mai tsanani (SARS) da cutar numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS) sun juya yanayin don bayyana yadda kamuwa da cutar HCoV ke iya zama mai hallaka da kuma kisa.
Yawancin kwayar cutar HCoVs daga ƙwararrun ƙwayoyin cuta ne.
An kuma san masu watsa kwayar cutar HCoVs.
Gano mai watsa labaran dabbobi yana da tasiri kai tsaye a kan rigakafin cututtuka a cikin mutane.
Binciken hulɗar CoV-mai masaukin baki a cikin dabbobi na iya ba da damar fahimtar CoV a cikin mutane.
Bisa ga bambancin jerin sunayen sunadarai, an rarraba CoVs zuwa jinsi huɗu (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV, da delta-CoV). Tsarin Beta-CoV ya ƙunshi yawancin HCoVs kuma an rarraba shi zuwa jinsi huɗu (A, B, C, da D).
Shaida ta ilimin halittu ta nuna cewa namomin kaza da masu ci suna da matsayin tushen kwayoyin halittar alpha-CoVs da beta-CoVs, yayin da tsuntsaye su ne manyan wuraren samun gamma-CoVs da delta-CoVs.
An san mutane bakwai da ke dauke da kwayar cutar HCoVs.
A cikin su, HCoV-229E da HCoV-NL63 sune alpha-CoVs.
Sauran beta-CoVs guda biyar sun hada da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, cutar rashin numfashi mai tsanani (SARS-CoV), cutar rashin numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS-CoV), da kuma SARS-CoV-2.
Binciken asalin kwayar cutar HCoV na dabbobi yana ba da tsari don fahimtar tarihin halitta, abubuwan motsawa, da abubuwan da ke hana ƙetare shingen nau'in.
Hakanan zai iya jagorantar ko sauƙaƙa bincike na mai watsa shiri, matsakaici da mai haɓaka SARS-CoV-2, tare da muhimman abubuwan da zai iya haifar da rigakafin kamuwa da cuta a nan gaba.
An san cewa akwai kwayar cutar dabbobi tun daga ƙarshen shekarun 1930.
An gano kwayar cutar HCoV guda bakwai a cikin shekarun baya bayan nan.
An fara gano kwayar HCoV-229E a cikin hanyoyin numfashi na marasa lafiya da ke da kamuwa da cutar numfashi a shekarar 1966, sannan kuma ta daidaita don girma a cikin layin ƙwayar WI-38 na huhu.
Marasa lafiya da ke dauke da cutar HCoV-229E suna da alamun sanyi na yau da kullun, gami da ciwon kai, tari, rashin jin daɗi da ciwon makogwaro, tare da zazzabi da tari a kashi 10 zuwa 20 cikin dari na masu cutar.
HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43 duk suna ko'ina a duniya kuma suna iya yaduwa a lokutan sanyi a ƙasashen da ke da yanayin zafi.
