WHO ta lura da bambanci tsakanin annobar SARS ta 2002-2004, inda aka zargi hukumomin China da ɓoyewa da ta hana hana rigakafin cutar da kuma magance ta, da kuma matsalar yanzu, inda gwamnatin tsakiya ta ba da rahotanni na yau da kullum don kauce wa fargaba a ranar Sabuwar Shekara ta Lunar.
