Kula da cutar COVID-19 a wurin aiki
Kula da hadarin COVID-19 a wurin aiki na nufin aiwatar da hanyoyin lafiya da tsaro a wurin aiki don kula da hadarin don rigakafin cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Kulawa mai kyau na haɗarin aiki ya bambanta dangane da wurin aiki da ayyuka, bisa la'akari da ƙimar haɗarin tushen haɗari, tsananin cutar a cikin al'umma, da kuma abubuwan haɗarin ma'aikata na mutum da ke iya zama mai saukin kamuwa da cutar COVID-19.
A cewar Hukumar Kula da Lafiya da Lafiya ta Aikin Aiki (OSHA) a Amurka, ayyuka da ke da ƙananan haɗarin kamuwa da cutar suna da ƙarancin hulɗa da jama'a da sauran ma'aikata. A wannan yanayin, ana ba da shawarar kawai matakan rigakafin kamuwa da cuta, gami da wanke hannu, ƙarfafa ma'aikata su zauna a gida idan suna da rashin lafiya, da kuma kiyaye tsabtace aiki da kuma tsabtace yanayin aiki.
Ayyuka masu haɗarin matsakaici sun haɗa da waɗanda ke buƙatar yawan ko kusanci da mutanen da ba su da COVID-19 da ake zargi ko saninsu, amma waɗanda za su iya kamuwa da cutar saboda yaduwar al'umma ko kuma tafiya ta duniya.
Wannan ya haɗa da ma'aikata da suke hulɗa da jama'a musamman a makarantu, wuraren aiki masu yawan jama'a da kuma wasu wuraren sayar da kaya masu yawa.
Kula da haɗari a cikin wannan rukunin, ban da matakan rigakafin kamuwa da cuta na asali, sun haɗa da iska ta amfani da matattarar iska mai inganci, gilashin tsabta, da samar da kayan kariya na mutum idan aka haɗu da mutumin da ke da COVID-19.
LOSHA ta ɗauki ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya da na jana'iza da ke fuskantar mutane da ake zargi ko kuma aka san suna da cutar COVID-19 a matsayin masu haɗarin haɗari, zuwa haɗarin gaske idan suna yin hanyoyin samar da iska ko kuma ɗaukar ko sarrafa samfurori daga mutanen da ake zargi ko aka san suna da cutar COVID-19.
